summary: Opinion: I’m kind of glad that in Into the Spider-verse Spider-Gwen’s Doctor Octopus didn’t have the actual tentacles that I’ve...
body:
Opinion:

I’m kind of glad that in Into the Spider-verse Spider-Gwen’s Doctor Octopus didn’t have the actual tentacles that I’ve heard he’s supposed to have (actually a literal pet octopus but okay).

Gwen’s thirteen years old. This is her first movie appearance. And if there were actual tentacles, I feel like that the hent@i-style fanart wouldn’t have been far off. So… it’s the small mercies.
